Business Brief -- U S West Inc.:
   Retirement Incentives Set
   For 2,400 Workers at Unit
The offer begins March 1. U S West has a total of 56,000
employees.
   Under the offer, the company will add three years to an
eligible employee's length of service for purposes of pension
calculations. The discount currently subtracted from the
monthly benefits of employees who retire early will be
eliminated, and the company will provide a 15% monthly
supplement to pension checks for employees younger than 62
until they begin to receive Social Security benefits.